openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Testcase API
  version: 2.0.0
paths:
  '/endpoint':
    get:
      parameters:
        - name: type
          in: query
          example: fruit
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - fruit
              - vegetable
              - drink
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 200 response
